{"tid":2053610,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"VB超新手功課求救","createTime":"2020-06-06T12:07:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T16:41:14.000Z","uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"18a016a1bcce303d141bfaed638c684cda4cf5ea","tid":2053610,"uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwXFMHv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwXFMHv.jpg&h=e5afc745&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zVBbTnu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzVBbTnu.jpg&h=d087d0cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問吓要點樣加入一個picbox被選擇嘅動作係中間？搞咗兩日重做咗n次都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後做到得個計算器...<br />\n唔知可以點插picbox<br />\n<br />\nPublic Class Form1<br />\n    Private Sub B1_Click(ByVal sender As System.Object, ByVal e As System.EventArgs) Handles B1.Click<br />\n        Dim data1, data2, data3, p As Integer<br />\n        If IsNumeric(txtb1.Text) And IsNumeric(txtb2.Text) And IsNumeric(txtb3.Text) Then<br />\n            data1 = txtb1.Text<br />\n            data2 = txtb2.Text<br />\n            data3 = txtb3.Text<br />\n            p = Data1 + Data2 + data3<br />\n            B1.Text = &quot;周界 = &quot; &amp; p<br />\n        Else<br />\n            MsgBox(&quot;請在空格內輸入數字!&quot;)<br />\n        End If<br />\n    End Sub<br />\nEnd Class"},{"pid":"c6ca24bb21bd2b564203f077e2eded32e5af5225","tid":2053610,"uid":120627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"唔知你講乜"},{"pid":"3d07a7132f798bfdd9ab5db864f76deae3e4f549","tid":2053610,"uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c6ca24bb21bd2b564203f077e2eded32e5af5225","tid":2053610,"uid":120627,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:18:19.000Z","msg":"唔知你講乜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T12:43:52.000Z","msg":"條題目要有6張圖<br />\n每揀一張圖下面打長寬計周長<br />\n<br />\n我只係做到揀完圖但計唔到<br />\nor<br />\n計完無揀到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知點先可以一齊做"},{"pid":"a6080471f0a7ae9e0dbdd6a379522163da12a3a2","tid":2053610,"uid":105464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:53:22.000Z","msg":"你係個label show 唔到定點<br />\nLabel直接係點擊picture個陣改<br />\n<br />\n移picture去中間個話<br />\n三張圖加個panel包住佢<br />\n一樣都係點擊picture個陣改<br />\n<br />\n一點擊個陣先拎依家張圖個location<br />\n用for each 搵圖個location係咪中間<br />\nE.g<br />\nDim c As Picturebox<br />\nFor Each c In Panel1.Controls<br />\nCheck location係咪中間<br />\n係的話就改做你原本既location <br />\n再張依家張圖 個location 改做中間個位"},{"pid":"eb26ca38518433827d54aa400e43b29f6d0935de","tid":2053610,"uid":42316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"最簡單做法，自己諗下點轉返vb 啦。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hfhng1m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfhng1m.png&h=99b689b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzeH1s6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzeH1s6.png&h=2225e77c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5655799b6bac284798bd500a54a3fbf0d4af5c6a","tid":2053610,"uid":280551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:23:16.000Z","msg":"題外話 <br />\n連登定律：vb一概負皮"},{"pid":"1768d5ab8eb9ec9657027a583563c81b4acdc88b","tid":2053610,"uid":130702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb26ca38518433827d54aa400e43b29f6d0935de","tid":2053610,"uid":42316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"最簡單做法，自己諗下點轉返vb 啦。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hfhng1m.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHfhng1m.png&h=99b689b8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SzeH1s6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSzeH1s6.png&h=2225e77c&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"巴打好多謝你 做好咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n猶如再生父母 好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}